title: Jerry Hsu Talks Emerica - The Hsu G6 - MADE Chapter 2
description:
Jerry talks about his history with Emerica, his new Hsu G6 shoe, and an update on MADE Chapter 2.

The Hsu G6 is the lightest Mid on the market and is available now at #HigherQuality skate shops everywhere.
